{\fscx80\fscy80}And it's not heaven that's worrying me...{\r}

287
00:28:11,889 --> 00:28:14,016
因为我没想到 我要面对这一切的
{\fscx80\fscy80}because I don't expect I'll ever have to face it.{\r}

288
00:28:14,091 --> 00:28:16,525
