{\fscx80\fscy80}Hmm? Yes.{\r}

354
00:31:46,804 --> 00:31:49,364
现在你去看看罗杰斯夫人 说了些什么
{\fscx80\fscy80}Now, you just trot down and see what Mrs. Rogers has to say.{\r}

355
00:31:49,439 --> 00:31:52,806
-不如先埋了哈里？ -明智！
