{\fscx80\fscy80}Forgetting a little detail like that could hang a man.{\r}

357
00:31:56,113 --> 00:31:58,013
对
{\fscx80\fscy80}[Chuckles] Yes.{\r}

358
00:32:34,251 --> 00:32:37,243
噢，噢.不好意思
{\fscx80\fscy80}Oh. Oh, I beg your pardon.{\r}

359
00:32:48,398 --> 00:32:51,663
